0.3
 - All headers use 'h' as extension
 - Moved helper functions (e.g. `normalize`) to M3d namespace
 - Added Vec4::toVec3
 - Dependency files for tests only depend on headers
 - Using 'bin' for build directory

0.2.1
 - Fixed Vec3::Vec3(double) not initializing fields

0.2
 - Added equality operators to Mat3 and Mat4

0.1.1
 - Fixed pkg-config file not using major version

0.1
 - Added 3x3 and 4x4 matrices
 - Added 3- and 4-component vectors
 - Added quaternion implementation
 - Added Math utility with some common constants and functions
